Happy Birthdayyyy chaneeee💗
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Happy Birthday Chaneee💗. The start has never been an end yet. 15 years and counting, can't be more greatful and happy for such a strong friendship. From you being so supportive and so crazy with me and all the sad stories I shared and how you made me feel they were shit for me personally. How we back bitched together about few people in our lives , which I truly enjoyed🙊😂. Thank you for the loyalty you gave me and the love you gave me💗. Thank you dost , you are the oldest friend of mine and not just friend, my family❤️. We’ve shared family moments together😌🥰. Our bond is stronger than anything and I wish it to be the same❤️. Thank you chaneeee and I miss you, meet soon and please eat less already mota ho chuka hai tu😂. I love you mere bhai💗. May you get immense success in your life and you achieve what you really want❤️. @raghavrajverma_

latestIgtvVideos.title: Bunuuuuu ka Birthday😍❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Happy Birthday Bunuu❤️. You’ve been special for me since a good time now, I do have a special reason for it but it stays with me always. You’re the only crazy women I know and I always see myself in you which makes me more comfortable than normal. I love the fact , that how cool you are and how much you don’t give a damn shit about others. Keeping that aside i know how you are and I also know the hidden you. I know the difficult story behind that pretty smile. I’ll always be there for you, not just for the sake but genuinely. I love you bunuu❤️. And I miss you a lot. Thank you for everything you’ve done and which you possibly could🤗❤️. Yours truly, Chatankiiiii👭. @mehvish_mishi
